  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/path-paris-obama-and-xi-invite-stronger-global-climate-ambition">On the Path to Paris, Obama and Xi Invite Stronger Global Climate Ambition</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/Obama&#32;Xi&#32;table.jpg" alt="" title="" width="200" height="119" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
