  <div class="views-field-field-library-file-fid">
                <div class="field-content"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>The latest <a href="https://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2015/09/25/us-china-joint-presidential-statement-climate-change">Obama-Xi announcement</a> sends a strong message: the two nations are acting fast to enable a global low carbon transition. Friday‚Äôs joint announcement is an unprecedented step by the world‚Äôs #1 and #2 emitters to commit, at the highest levels, to a strong set of domestic policies and to reinforce global mechanisms that will help to engage peers ahead of the upcoming landmark climate change negotiations in Paris.</p></div>
