  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/chinas-new-energy-consumption-control-target">China‚Äôs New Energy Consumption Control Target</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/Shuozhou_coal_power_plant2.jpg" alt="" title="" width="160" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-library-file-fid">
                <div class="field-content"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>China‚Äôs State Council in late January <a href="http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/china/2013-01/30/c_132139588.htm">approved</a>  an ‚Äúenergy consumption control target‚Äù to keep the country‚Äôs total energy consumption below the equivalent of 4 billion tonnes of coal per year by 2015.</p></div>
  </div>
