  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/towards-china-environmental-performance-index">Towards a China Environmental Performance Index</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/Thumbnail_EPI_1.png" alt="" title="" width="79" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-library-file-fid">
                <div class="field-content"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>ChinaFAQs expert Angel Hsu and her colleagues from the Yale Center for Environmental Law and Policy team up with Columbia University, Chinese Academy for Environmental Planning and City University of Hong Kong for <a href="http://environment.yale.edu/envirocenter/files/China-EPI-Report.pdf">this report</a> to help guide effective pollution control and natural resource management.</p></div>
